>I'm not really on FA or twitter
Most artists are on those sites and network commissions through those. A lot of them also open commissions only for a short period of time, usually about one day, and then close and sort through entries. So you’re gonna have to pay attention to the ones you wanna commission if you want a chance.
My best suggestion would be to find good art on someplace like e621, see if the artist takes commissions, and ask or see if they’re open. Sometimes, they’ll do a commission even if they say they’re closed if you just ask, that’s how my first one happened.
